Legible Text Context

I used the default font that Android Studio suggested as it is simple to read and very clear, it is also a universal font so its made for clarity to anyone using the app. The font size is large enough for the user to view and read all the prompts and button as well as result view.

Make interface Elements clearly visible.

All the components are readily available to the user immediately when the app is started, there is enough text padding and space with appropriate spelling.
